<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; }
    .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 32px; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; }
    h1 { color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 22px; }
    .credential { background: #f0f0f0; border-radius: 4px; padding: 12px 16px; margin: 8px 0; font-family: monospace; font-size: 15px; }
    .label { font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 24px; font-size: 12px; color: #999; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Welcome to the race, {{fullName}}!</h1>
    <p>Your registration for <strong>{{raceName}}</strong> has been confirmed. Here are your login credentials for the participant dashboard:</p>

    <div class="label">Email</div>
    <div class="credential">{{email}}</div>

    <div class="label">Password</div>
    <div class="credential">{{password}}</div>

    <p>Use these to log in and track your upcoming races, results, and stats.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      Please keep this email safe. If you did not register for this event, you can ignore this message.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
